# Copy to scripts/.scrub-patterns (gitignored) and add site-specific regexes,
# one extended-regex per line. The scrub gate loads these IN ADDITION to the
# built-in generic secret/IP/username checks. Put anything identifying that is
# NOT auto-derivable here -- your internal domain, an old leaked secret prefix,
# a project codename, etc. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Examples (edit for your environment; do NOT leave these literally):
#   your-internal-domain\.lan
#   my-old-hostname
#   deadbeef            # first bytes of a rotated secret you want to be sure is gone
